Description: We invite you to classes that will allow you to fully enjoy life and feel better in your own body. Thanks to "Fitness with Kasia" you will gain not only better fitness, but also positive energy and motivation for further activities. Classes are conducted in a friendly atmosphere, and Kasia is always available to help and advise. Join us today and see how many benefits regular training can bring!
Name: Fitness with Kasia
Pricing: 20 PLN single entry, monthly ticket available cheaper
